DATA & METHODOLOGY DISCLAIMER

This software uses publicly available regulatory documents, industry reports,
and market data including but not limited to:

  - EU Regulation (EU) 2023/956 and Implementing Regulations
  - ICAP (International Carbon Action Partnership) data
  - KOTRA, 한국무역협회 (KITA), 대한상공회의소 SGI reports
  - POSCO, Hyundai Steel, Hanwha, SK ESG / Climate Risk disclosures
  - IEA, IEAGHG, NETL, World Steel Association technical reports
  - EEX, ICE, Sandbag carbon market data

All numbers are estimates based on publicly available information at the
time of last update. Users should validate with their own verified data
before making business decisions. This tool is for educational and
analytical purposes only and does not constitute financial, legal, or
regulatory advice.
